Title: A uniform model of the massive spinning particle in any dimension
Authors: S. L. Lyakhovich, A. A. Sharapov, K. M. Shekhter
Comments: Latex, revised version of hep-th/9811003
Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A15 (2000) 4287-4300
\\
  The general model of an arbitrary spin massive particle in any dimensional
space-time is derived on the basis of Kirillov - Kostant - Souriau approach. It
is shown that the model allows consistent coupling to an arbitrary background
of electromagnetic and gravitational fields.
